 <summary>A finite state machine</summary>
 <description>Stagehand_FSM is a finite state machine.

Using Stagehand_FSM with applications, frameworks, and toolkits, it can make to simplify complex state management code in them. And also, it can be used as an engine of event-driven architecture.</description>
